Text: How are you still standing?
Defeat Wicked Thunder
Let the victor's reign be sanctioned by the blood of the fallen.
I need more power!
Graaah... Hraaah... Hraaagh!
More! I need more!
What visions are these?
Out of my way!
Is this my weakness, given shape?
Down with you!
No limits will bind me!
Begone, along with my pitiful past!
Yaaaaaarrrgh!
You're in my way... All of you, in my way!
I am the worthy king!
There is no miracle!
I trust only in myself!
This is my path!
Hahahahaha! It's mine─the ultimate power!
This power is proof of my authority!
Creation yields to my command!
My will resonates within reality!
All is mine to make and unmake!
Such might befits a ruler─befits me!
Protect the Temple Knights!
Defeat Leophyne!
Brace yourself against the power of the artifact!
Protect Tentoawa!
Give back the cradle or we'll take it back!
All bluster, as usual. Take it if you dare!
Protect the netherling warriors!
The Zundu! With them by our side, Leophyne won't stand a chance!
Why must you resist? Succumb to the burden of sleep, and dream eternal.
Now! Wash away darkness of sleep with sundrop dance!
Don't just stand there! Kill them!
<split(<Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight>, ,1)>, defend our allies over there! I'll take the other side!
Everyone's awake!
Mighty Zundu protect netherling warriors! Keep cautious, like gaelicat under stormy skies!
Heh, now you're all alone. This ends now, Leophyne!
Why am I cursed with incompetents? Very well...dance with me, Wide Eye!
I have yet to test the strength granted to me...your strength. Now I shall!
The artifact isn't for such callous hands!
The narwhal's blessing is only for those with the heart of a defender!
Be undone!
That's it, <split(<Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight>, ,1)>!
To think it could hold such immense power... Hahaha!
<split(<Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight>, ,1)>, we need to split up! You take that side!
Thank you both! Healing is on the way!
I am far from finished. You will not withstand this!
Others are just tools to you. Is that your idea of freedom!?
I'll protect you...until my last breath!
Gaaahhh!
I'm all right. What about Tentoawa!?
You think this piece of wood is for protection? Such a cloying sentiment...
Cursed insects... You lot, finish them off! Earn your freedom!
Sundrop dance shall rouse netherling warrior! Protect the sleeper until he awakens!
It's time for us to protect Tentoawa! We'll get through this together!
On your feet, Tentoawa! It's your duty as the Wide Eye!
I owe you all my life. Thank you!
Zundu go to help allies! May zephyr winds guide you to victory!
No... Sleep is inexorable... How are they doing this!?
It's just as I said─sleep is absolute! No living thing can resist its call!
Witness the sundrop dance! Netherling warriors, awaken!
Another one falls. Life is ever so fleeting!
I hope you're ready to be ripped to shreds!
Our challenger's first opponent: Black Cat!
Can they hold their own against her feline ferocity!?
These claws rend all!
Here it comes! Black Cat's lithe and lethal maneuver!
My riiing!
Ahem. Please bear with us while we repair the ring.
I sharpened these just for you!
Can you dodge this, I wonder.
I'll gut you like a cod!
Going up!
Coming down!
To me, echo of my soul!
Hah!
You're mincemeat!
Try this!
Defeat Black Cat
A vicious blow! That'll leave a mark!
Even I felt that one! But the challenger's still standing!
Beautifully dodged!
Amazing! The challenger saw straight through it!
Oh my! The challenger went down hard!
And they're down! Is it over already!?
They're back on their feet! What grit!
They're still in it! But for how long!?
What power! Looks like someone isn't holding back!
Such potent magicks! But will they be enough to turn the tide?
They're bracing for the storm with an ironclad defense!
Oh dear! The challenger has fallen out of the ring!
It's all over...until next time!
グ、ギィヤアアアア！
Ice shall be thy tomb!
プギャァアア！
グゥ、ググガアア……！
ギイィィィ！　ギイィィィ！
グギャ、ギャア……！
ピギィヤアアアアアアアアア！
ピィギィィ！
フグゥゥ……！
グゥゥギャア！
ギギ……ギィ！
ギ、ギャガァァァ！
フグゥゥ……フゥ、ギャア……！
